<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/848891-i-do-mostly-audiobooks-so-i-listened-to">I do mostly audiobooks, so I listened to Every Dead Thing and it was great, a very tight 4 hours in length. I see that Dark Hollow is listed as 14 hours. However, on Amazon their print length seems about the same, around 480 pages. What am I missing? Is Dark Hollow really 3+ times longer than Every Dead Thing?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
